metadata.name: Naruto
metadata.description: A signature work by artist MIHA, Mihaverse Butterfly is a contemporary art collection of 1111 pixelated emotive hand-painted animated butterflies inspired by concepts of transformation and mimicry. The first Butterfly NFT brand on the blockchain! Bringing to life pop culture classics: your favorite memes, emojis, and other parodies mounted on butterfly wings. Let's Fly!
